      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need help writing an email to a customer. They bought this really expensive espresso machine from us, but there was a logistics error and now the shipment is two weeks late. I need to apologize and explain it without sounding too incompetent, and maybe offer them a discount on their next order to make up for it. Can you give me a draft?",
